{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Abolish grammar schools & reallocate funding to SEND & mainstream schools",
        "additional_details": "Require local authorities to abolish the 11 plus & integrate funding into mainstream education support, specifically the Government\u2019s goal of providing core support for SEND within mainstream settings, ensuring more children can access multi-disciplinary services without needing lengthy statutory assessments. The government funding that we think is wasted on the 11 plus system can be used for other parts of the education system.",
        "background": "Require phase out of remaining state-funded selective grammar schools. Reallocate funding to SEND support. Require local authorities to redirect resources from selective testing (11 plus) toward an inclusive, mainstream-first education system.",
